    <item>
      <title>阿根廷官员称该国已偿还主权债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/argentina-official-says-country-made-payments-on-sovereign-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷在周四的最后期限之前向国际债券持有人支付了款项，这标志着总统哈维尔·米莱伊为恢复投资者对这个惯犯债务国的信心又迈出了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/argentina-official-says-country-made-payments-on-sovereign-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 13:24:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗公司的泽尔特认为私人和公共市场壁垒正在消失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/public-private-markets-barriers-to-fall-apollo-s-zelter-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司联席总裁詹姆斯泽尔特在接受彭博电视采访时表示，随着企业越来越多地受益于更广泛的融资选择，私人市场和公开市场之间的障碍正在减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/public-private-markets-barriers-to-fall-apollo-s-zelter-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 12:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国中型股止跌，欧洲股市因美国政策受关注而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/european-stocks-drop-amid-us-policy-jitters-uk-mid-caps-lag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国国内股指在因担心财政赤字和通胀上升而跌至 4 月以来最低点后有所回升。由于投资者关注美国贸易政策前景，泛欧基准指数上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/european-stocks-drop-amid-us-policy-jitters-uk-mid-caps-lag</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 08:13:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
