      <title>英国债券市场动荡令人回想起1976年债务危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-bond-turmoil-gives-labour-nightmare-of-britain-s-1976-debt-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最近的债券风暴让人联想到 2022 年利兹·特拉斯 (Liz Truss) 的迷你预算灾难，但将其与 20 世纪 70 年代的债务危机进行比较可能更为恰当。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-bond-turmoil-gives-labour-nightmare-of-britain-s-1976-debt-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国债结束四天抛售；英国资产暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受全球债券需求强劲信号的影响，美国国债本周首日上涨，结束了因投资者对政府债务和通胀上升的担忧而引发的抛售。英国资产继续遭受重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 22:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
